Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.39,0:24:19.85,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}状況は非科学的に
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.06,0:24:23.73,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}感情のモンタージュ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.94,0:24:26.44,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}誰が誰を呼んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.73,0:24:32.36,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}振り向けば　逃げてく視線　感じる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.61,0:24:34.91,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}気のせいじゃつれないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.95,0:24:39.99,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}アンテナは才能って言うでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.50,0:24:43.87,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}だってだって　知りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.12,0:24:45.63,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}君は違うの？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.71,0:24:52.38,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}青春の温度差　今のうち　正してあげるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.38,0:24:56.85,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}明日解決するなら　今でもよくない？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.97,0:25:02.60,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}君のミステリー　解いてみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.68,0:25:07.23,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}少年の秘密めいた背中探せ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.40,0:25:10.94,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今日も君はファンタジー
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.03,0:25:14.74,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}惹けれてゆくよ　ずるい
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.78,0:25:20.54,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}膨らんだ好奇心　トリックはないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.58,0:25:24.79,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}気になるよ　興味深い
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.91,0:25:27.38,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.39,0:24:19.85,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}狀況完全不科學
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.06,0:24:23.73,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}感情如拼貼畫般交織
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.94,0:24:26.44,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}是誰在將誰呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.73,0:24:32.36,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}回頭時感覺到你逃避的視線
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.61,0:24:34.91,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}說這是錯覺未免無情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.95,0:24:39.99,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}直覺該稱為才能才對
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.50,0:24:43.87,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}因為我想瞭解你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.12,0:24:45.63,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}難道你並非如此？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.71,0:24:52.38,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}現在就為你糾正青春的溫差
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.38,0:24:56.85,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}既然明天能解決 不如趁現在搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.97,0:25:02.60,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我想要解開你的懸疑
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.68,0:25:07.23,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}探尋少年神秘的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.40,0:25:10.94,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今天的你也如同幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.03,0:25:14.74,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}狡猾地吸引著我不斷沉迷
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.78,0:25:20.54,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}膨脹的好奇中分明不含心機
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.58,0:25:24.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}令人在意 耐人尋味
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.91,0:25:27.38,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}這究竟是為什麼
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,==========STORY==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.85,0:00:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們閒不閒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想成為神山市搶答王嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.28,0:00:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,區區預選賽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可要突破啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問答預選賽7！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:02.89,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,300)\blur3\pos(1395,918)}傍晚便成骸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一問
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金剛石就是鑽石 綠柱石就是祖母綠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是對的 還是錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一問大概就這水準了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:40.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我告訴你 誰才是真正的數據庫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人數越來越少了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這會是預選賽的最後一個問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 第七問
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:54.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「遲鈍」的語源是英語「dull」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:54.23,Default,NTP,0,600,0,,{\fs53}darui
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是對的還是錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:02:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哪個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺像是語源 不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.99,0:03:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼看 摩耶花？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得是對還是錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對的…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用賣關子了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,預選結束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:23.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜答對的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決賽將在這邊的檯子上進行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 請上台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福部 你打扮得挺有趣的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}這是第一位決賽選手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}請報上姓名和班級
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這人誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你完全沒注意到我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我光顧著答題了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 谷同學 圍棋部怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}不好意思 我有點緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圍棋部嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}那麼 繼續介紹第二位決賽選手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出了件有趣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要聽聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 下面是第三位決賽選手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:06.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這位選手頭上頂著土星呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請報上你的班級和姓名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是古典部的福部里志
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是古典部的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 還有叫古典部的社團啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個學校裡奇怪的社團不少嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 這是個奇怪的社團
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.54,0:04:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為連活動目的都是個問號
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為知道要製作文集 所以就做了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果做得還挺不錯的 花了很大力氣的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確花了很大力氣 在數量方面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:55.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文集裡揭示了KANYA祭的重大秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:04:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦！那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KANYA祭這個名字的由來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神山高中文化祭 簡稱KANYA祭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是這麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部把這個謎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,徹底揭開了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:17.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那由來是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:24.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就請大家去買吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要200日元
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就能得到神山高中文化祭45年來的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文集「冰菓」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於特別教學樓四樓 地理準備室絕讚發售中！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推銷成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優勝什麼的已經無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:50.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:05:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,田名邊學長說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以讓其他社團代售
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是我想去找入須學姐商量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻走不到那裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛 原因倒是猜得到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下頭疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:18.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里志的宣傳挺有趣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宣傳…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 我記得牆報部會發行號外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去問問他們能不能幫古典部寫篇報道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是忙碌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnWenQuanYi Micro Hei\c&H1A282C&\3c&HB8D9DD&\pos(954,162)}牆報部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnMingLiU\fs45\c&H1F3538&\3c&HCFEBEE&\pos(943.5,526.5)\b1}歡迎爆料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:45.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 遠垣內學長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能幫古典部寫篇報道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太明白你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想拜託你在牆報部的報道裡為古典部宣傳一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:14.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我已經不是部員了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經高三 所以退休了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 能幫我介紹一下後輩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那倒是可以 不過我覺得沒什麼用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們每兩小時就要發一份號外
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日程事先就決定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒法刊發…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可沒說沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二天中午之後版面應該會有餘地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是KANYA祭有50多個社團參加
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:47.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會優先報道那些值得關注的社團
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說可能有些失禮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我記得古典部只發行文集吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 文集的內容…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:07:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每個社團的內容都是認真準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有能吸引大家的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:04.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是可以拜託他們幫你寫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話題…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉佔用了你的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是發生了什麼有趣的事 就再來一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們說不定能幫得上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛琉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 華穗同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十文字伯伯之後還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經全好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來你好像悶悶不樂啊 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了一些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就進來 我幫你占卜一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是這麼厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 就用塔羅牌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:08:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛琉 我記得你喜歡這種吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnFZLiBian-S02\b0\fs60\c&H4A545A&\3c&HEAF1F6&\pos(613.5,295.5)}占卜研究會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnFZLiBian-S02\b0\fs60\c&H4A545A&\3c&HEAF1F6&\pos(667.5,498)}已失去命運之輪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnFZLiBian-S02\b0\fs60\c&H4A545A&\3c&HEAF1F6&\pos(1281,729)}十文字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,占卜研只有我一個人 所以我時常離開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去一會兒再回來之後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命運之輪這張塔羅牌就不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:26.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而現場則留下了這張卡片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十文字…為什麼會寫著華穗同學的姓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 究竟為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丟失的那張牌找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留在現場的還有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnFZLiBian-S02\b0\fs60\c&H4A545A&\3c&H7EE9F4&\pos(1032,718.5)}文化祭過後定當歸還。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我覺得應該會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個古怪的小偷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後再給你看一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\fs52.5\c&H3295DC&\3c&HCDEFEE&\b1\pos(930,786)}帶你漫步KANYA{\c&H616FD7&}祭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這本小冊子有什麼特別的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,內容和發下來的那本一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟那張卡放在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翻開在參加社團一句話評論的最後一頁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是有什麼意義呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要命運之輪好好還回來就滿意了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:26.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 終於進入高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清水同學 後藤同學各5分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而谷同學 福部同學各6分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們離優勝都只有一分之遙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最終結局將會如何發展呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請大家聲援他們！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 下一問
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,球體表面積的計算公式是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,４πｒ²
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 好快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:11:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問題還沒念完呢 沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼清水同學 請回答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3/4πｒ³
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,球體表面積的計算公式是４πｒ²
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼球體體積的計算公式是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案是3/4πｒ³ 非常精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來 清水同學離優勝也只差最後一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:43.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三位同學拿到6分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相當緊張刺激的平手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後藤同學也請加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 下一問
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.56,0:11:53.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神山高中學生會長的全名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:02.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請回答
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 清水同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陸山宗芳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別賣關子了行不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:18.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答對了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 福部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 我們都好遺憾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 居然平手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著說圍棋部的趣事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棋子被偷走了幾顆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 不是丟了而是被偷了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好笑的是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.03,0:12:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還收到了「圍棋部的棋子我拿走了」的犯罪聲明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟不會全都用到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以明明拿走十顆也沒人會發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷那種東西做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那自然是玩五子棋之類了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看是其他部員的惡作劇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平手實在不過癮 來分個高下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你接下來要參加什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.93,0:13:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天料理研的活動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK 這場比賽的勝負就留到那裡去分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不知趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:27.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}清水同學 你現在的心情如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對和谷同學比試沒興趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道奉太郎有沒有認真看店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有開張嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:13:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開 開著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫著KANYA祭由來的就是這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以翻翻看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:03.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.28,0:14:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,200日元而已 買回去看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,印得太多我們都要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學長 你石門水庫沒關
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 破掉了 麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請用這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 真虧你有這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是謝禮 給你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,氣槍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.69,0:14:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是水槍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,園藝部在烤白薯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滅火要是拿水桶就太沒意思了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:14:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那這個你們不是需要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:01.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是輔助兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主武器是這個 AK的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我走啦 謝嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格洛克17嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:15.51,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：奧地利格洛克公司設計生產的第一枝手槍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:19.02,inter,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs150\pos(1100,178)\blur2}秋 分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:19.02,inter,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(472,342)\blur2}晝夜等長日 乃是秋分時
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底 這本文集就很失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就沒人來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是趁現在畫張海報吸引客人比較好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 是大家決定用這種風格的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要看我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一百部漫畫的評論什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:52.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種死板的東西誰要看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.51,0:15:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 河內同學 少說兩句吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:15:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底 評論什麼的根本沒意義
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒用的沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:02.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿福會相信我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.24,0:16:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是真的不想惹事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒用是什麼意思 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一言以蔽之 就是讀者的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讀者？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有漫畫的趣味性原本就是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是誰畫的都一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 有趣與否的區別體現在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.66,0:16:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不明白嗎 伊原
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:00.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就在於讀者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底 就是取決於讀者對趣味性的敏感度而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 敏感度低的人無法體會到趣味性嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:17.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才說評論是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只要讀自己喜歡的作品 哈哈大笑就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的漫畫都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:31.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種觀點我絕對無法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不會認輸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照你的邏輯 所謂的名作也是不存在的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:41.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名作當然是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,定義呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長年累月經過眾多讀者篩選而留存下來的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是名作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:18:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名作一誕生就是名作了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種沒經過時間考驗的東西…你這才叫主觀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.77,0:18:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是經驗問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學姐你只是沒看到過讓你怦然心動 覺得很了不起的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真敢說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作者的才能和技巧之差絕對是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:33.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學姐 去年在這所學校的文化祭上出售的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名叫「傍晚便成骸」的漫畫 你看過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我明天帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那樣你還不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無話可說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來 代售「冰菓」的事就徹底說不出口了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:18:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fs45\c&H131517&\3c&HBAC0C2&\frz270\pos(1305,660)}不可錯過! 正在決戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fs45\c&H131517&\3c&HBAC0C2&\frz270\pos(1122,648)}少女之戰in漫研
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fs45\c&H131517&\frz270\pos(811.5,594)\3c&HC3C7C9&}漫畫論激辯中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fs45\c&H131517&\3c&HBAC0C2&\frz270\pos(516,648)}巫女VS雙性體
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:14.38,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：伊原COS的角色在其原作中是雙性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少女之戰…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:16.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天還會繼續 請務必來參觀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的宣傳多少派上點用場了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賣了14本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的宣傳好像意外地有效
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭一炮算是打得很不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天再努力一把吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,料理競賽我還是有自信的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個三人一組的比賽？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 三人一組？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:20:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身為總務委員 卻沒把活動情況掌握清楚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,增加攤點和讓牆報部報道我們 我都沒辦到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別介意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 有件事我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.57,0:20:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很在意？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 還是…不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 沒寫三人一組啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是三人一組 我聽到料理研的人這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 失算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為可以一個人出戰的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說來 摩耶花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漫研怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩耶花 千反田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.19,0:20:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能陪我一起參加料理研的競賽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是可以跟部長商量 請她讓我中途離開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能起到宣傳效果 我也想參加
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 總之湊到人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.54,0:21:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是有多想參加啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對料理還是有點自信的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:19.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼好玩的大賽怎麼能不去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.84,0:21:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}全校同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}以及前來參觀的遊客請注意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.18,0:21:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}本廣播宣佈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.31,0:21:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}KANYA祭第一天的日程到此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}還留在校內的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 折木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:45.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}請儘快關好門窗 離開學校
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 不…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.26,0:22:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.72,0:22:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.28,0:23:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用這個代替吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.53,0:23:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.37,0:23:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.24,0:23:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.58,0:24:00.54,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3\fs48\pos(722,890)}歡迎來到KANYA祭！
